the mountains' spine ♪

601
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:01,350
Six months later,

602
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:02,700
under the leadership of the anti-Japanese
democratic government,

603
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:05,090
♪ Holding up the undying sun ♪

604
00:28:05,090 --> 00:28:06,150
our village established a village office.

605
00:28:06,150 --> 00:28:07,550
♪ Gifting us spring light
and wheat waves ♪

606
00:28:07,550 --> 00:28:09,870
Chang Chun and Kejin
brought a work team

607
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:12,240
and stationed themselves in our village.

608
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,550
According to Wendian's last wish,

609
00:28:13,550 --> 00:28:14,330
[News]

610
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:17,590
