Kejin kept part of the house
for Yinzi and Keyu.

613
00:28:22,500 --> 00:28:24,330
[Democratic Election]

614
00:28:24,330 --> 00:28:26,960
-The rest of the house
-Comrade Tietou

615
00:28:26,990 --> 00:28:29,610
-elected as the village secretary.
-became the headquarters

616
00:28:29,610 --> 00:28:31,620
of the farmers' association and militia.

617
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:33,300
Great!

618
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,440
Comrade Feng Ziyong

619
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:38,520
has been elected as

620
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:40,410
the Chief of Ox Temple Village!

621
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,550
Great!

622
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:47,000
Great!

623
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:51,510
The candidates for militia captain

624
00:28:51,510 --> 00:28:52,510
are

625
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:55,750
Niu Tianxiu, Sun Changjiang,
