626
00:28:55,770 --> 00:28:57,240
Great!

627
00:28:57,370 --> 00:28:59,320
The candidates for women's team leader are

628
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:01,160
Ning Xiuxiu and Niu Chunhua.

629
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:01,770
Great!

630
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:09,440
My father has been gone
for over half a year now.

631
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:11,320
You've been living quietly with Keyu,

632
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:12,690
keeping to yourself

633
00:29:13,370 --> 00:29:15,230
without staying in touch with us.

634
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,300
I know

635
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:18,500
