638
00:29:23,330 --> 00:29:25,260
and you won't let Keyu go to school.

639
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,340
I've asked around for you.

640
00:29:28,650 --> 00:29:31,280
The county middle school
starts entrance exams next month.

641
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:33,110
You should take him there at that time.

642
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:35,110
If he passes, he can board at school.

643
00:29:35,430 --> 00:29:36,710
Once he's gone,

644
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,320
