653
00:30:09,650 --> 00:30:10,920
If I respond, do you dare to call me that?

654
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,510
Mother.

655
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,970
You really responded?

656
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,030
Stepmother.

657
00:30:15,050 --> 00:30:15,640
Daughter.

658
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,440
Stepmother.

659
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,270
Daughter.

660
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:19,530
Give me my New Year's money, Stepmother.

661
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,500
Thank you, Xiu.

662
00:30:22,930 --> 00:30:24,660
You're taking advantage of me.

663
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,240
By all rights,

664
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:33,350
since you married my father,

665
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:35,810
I should be the last person to advise you.

666
00:30:36,160 --> 00:30:37,750
But I still want to tell you

667
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,160
that your life

668
00:30:40,090 --> 00:30:42,090
should be in your own hands.

669
00:30:43,260 --> 00:30:45,260
You need to find your own way to live.

670
00:30:46,120 --> 00:30:47,510
You're still so young.

671
00:30:48,010 --> 00:30:50,670
Don't label yourself
as Ning Xuexiang's widow,

672
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:53,340
remaining a widow
for the rest of your life.

673
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:55,920
Yinzi.

674
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:58,030
Listen to me.

675
00:30:58,770 --> 00:31:00,500
You need to live in the present,

676
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:03,050
From now on, live every day

677
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:05,440
as Fei Yinzi's own day.

678
00:31:06,790 --> 00:31:07,880
From now on,

679
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,680
live every day

680
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:10,200
as Fei Yinzi's own day?

681
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:14,630
Live as Fei Yinzi.

682
00:31:15,910 --> 00:31:17,070
That means living

683
00:31:18,410 --> 00:31:19,440
as myself?

684
00:31:35,930 --> 00:31:36,750
Take it easy!

685
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:37,410
Okay.

686
00:31:38,350 --> 00:31:39,070
I'm fine.

687
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,960
Don't rush.

688
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:49,550
Everyone, take a break!

689
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,350
Come have some water!

690
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:52,720
Okay, coming!

691
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:54,160
Come drink water!

692
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:55,680
Come on, have some water.

693
00:31:56,090 --> 00:31:57,130
Come drink.

694
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:12,160
You've worked hard.

695
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:12,960
It's nothing.

696
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:15,620
Xiuxiu.

697
00:32:15,970 --> 00:32:17,250
So much has grown.

698
00:32:30,270 --> 00:32:30,920
Tietou,

699
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:32,030
have some water.

700
00:32:32,060 --> 00:32:32,990
I don't want any.

701
00:32:34,870 --> 00:32:35,380
Here.

702
00:32:43,510 --> 00:32:45,270
Tietou, come have some water!

703
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,480
Wait.

704
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:49,030
I'll finish plowing this patch first.

705
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:56,730
When I was young, I hated land.

706
00:32:57,260 --> 00:33:01,890
