709
00:33:08,190 --> 00:33:09,670
We're all attached to it.

710
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,920
The land doesn't speak.

711
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:15,060
Whether I resented it or loved it,

712
00:33:15,250 --> 00:33:17,750
it still silently grew crops,

713
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:21,880
nourishing us and all living things,

714
00:33:22,110 --> 00:33:26,960
eternal and everlasting.

715
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:30,350
Why are you back so late?

716
00:33:30,580 --> 00:33:32,690
September 1964,

717
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:35,280
