718
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:38,210
Take off those wet clothes
before you catch cold.

719
00:33:38,210 --> 00:33:41,140
I'm going to drain water
from the sweet potato field.

720
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:42,640
This rain

721
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:44,360
