will rot in the field.

725
00:33:50,230 --> 00:33:51,110
Where are you going?

726
00:33:51,110 --> 00:33:52,590
Have your meal first.

727
00:33:52,930 --> 00:33:54,410
The Shu River is flooding.

728
00:33:54,570 --> 00:33:55,700
I need to go check it.

729
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:57,230
I can't let the water

730
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,940
flow back into our fields.

731
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:00,500
Go ahead and eat. Don't wait for me.

732
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:01,500
I'll be back soon.

733
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:03,480
The rain is so heavy outside.

734
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:05,200
You can barely see the path.

735
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:07,480
Be careful with your failing eyesight.

736
00:34:08,219 --> 00:34:09,409
Don't worry, dear.

737
00:34:10,130 --> 00:34:13,020
I know the village roads so well
I could walk them with my eyes closed.

738
00:34:13,020 --> 00:34:14,650
take good care of the children.

739
00:34:14,650 --> 00:34:16,880
They're grown up now.
They don't need looking after.

740
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,880
No matter how old,

741
00:34:18,110 --> 00:34:19,550
