742
00:34:20,139 --> 00:34:20,870
I'm leaving.

743
00:34:28,790 --> 00:34:32,580
After my Dajiao left that day,

744
00:34:32,870 --> 00:34:35,020
he never came back.

745
00:34:35,710 --> 00:34:37,909
He led people to protect the dam

746
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:40,030
and saved the farmland.

747
00:34:40,780 --> 00:34:43,050
He was the old production team leader,

748
00:34:43,730 --> 00:34:45,960
but he was swept away

749
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,280
by the raging flood.

750
00:35:04,910 --> 00:35:06,350
In the spring of 1986,

751
00:35:06,580 --> 00:35:09,310
the winds of reform swept across China.

752
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:10,800
The Ning Residence and

753
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,810
the surviving neighboring houses

754
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,590
of Ox Temple Village

755
