759
00:35:26,390 --> 00:35:28,070
It also became

760
00:35:28,090 --> 00:35:30,610
a highlighted special exhibit

761
00:35:30,790 --> 00:35:32,230
for visitors.

762
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:33,790
Let's look behind us.

763
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:34,550
That building

764
00:35:34,550 --> 00:35:35,960
was built later to celebrate

765
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,630
the 60th anniversary
of the Communist Party

766
00:35:37,630 --> 00:35:38,950
of China.

767
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,600
In my dreams,

768
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,560
I've lost count of how many times

769
00:35:57,840 --> 00:36:00,450
I've stepped through this door
just like this.

770
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:09,240
Just like this,

771
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:12,730
walking on the bluestone-paved path
in the courtyard.

772
00:36:17,650 --> 00:36:18,890
In my dreams,

773
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:22,780
I can smell the odor of cattle

774
